column1: : This file has a line entry for each filter, by name and functionality.
:   The data is stored in comma delimited colums -
:   'Name','Action Set','Action Name', reserved, reserved, reserved, reserved
: The following are the internal Visual Basic variables that receive this file data, with comments.
: FilterName(64) As String           ' name of the filter
: FilterSetName(64) As String        ' photoshop action set name that this filter action is found in
